methods.axisTransform:
Returns an axis transform.

:param name: (java.lang.String) - case insensitive transform name.
:return: (io.deephaven.plot.axistransformations.AxisTransform) requested axis transform.
methods.axisTransformNames:
Returns the names of available axis transforms.

:return: (java.lang.String[]) an array of the available axis transform names.
methods.inverseTransform:
Transforms a point in Axis space to dataset space.

:param axisValue: (double) - Axis space data point
:return: (double) corresponding value in dataset space
methods.isVisible:
Gets whether a data point is visible in the plot.

:param dataValue: (double) - data point
:return: (boolean) whether dataValue is visible in the plot
methods.transform:
Transforms a data point to Axis space.

:param dataValue: (double) - data point
:return: (double) corresponding value in Axis space
methods.valueOf:
Returns the enum constant of this type with the specified name.
The string must match exactly an identifier used to declare an
enum constant in this type.  (Extraneous whitespace characters are 
not permitted.)

:param name: (java.lang.String) - the name of the enum constant to be returned.
:return: (io.deephaven.plot.axistransformations.AxisTransforms) the enum constant with the specified name
methods.values:
Returns an array containing the constants of this enum type, in
the order they are declared.

:return: (io.deephaven.plot.axistransformations.AxisTransforms[]) an array containing the constants of this enum type, in the order they are declared
